識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faac4aa4f3b24c949317b6252b0e288e29219511","tid":1355980,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"410e119fc806deb51c2bef9ca33c4d19a9371384","tid":1355980,"uid":87931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:44:04.000Z","msg":"對於球迷合唱一時，「Ken Sir」則表示歡迎，至於被問及會否擔心有球迷於場內高舉政治標語，他則表示若沒有構成場內保安風險，則問題不大︰「<span style=\"color: red;\">如果球迷嚟唱歌，我覺得係好事，首先球迷有一個表達，用歌聲去表達，呢個表達肯定係一個好嘅表達，因為唔係一個暴力嘅表達，所以大家嚟唱歌，我洗耳恭聽，絕對冇問題。</span>足球係生活裏面嘅一部份，大球場有一定保安嘅規矩，如果喺規矩容許之下去表達意見，我個人覺得冇問題。如果我哋有一場好精彩嘅比賽喺度進行緊，有人舉起標語畀人睇，我諗每一個觀眾都可以決定，究竟繼續睇場波定係睇住舉起標語嘅事情發生，我覺得呢個唔係一個好大嘅問題，當然我哋唔希望表達方式，會對場地保安方面有問題。」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開晒綠燈<br />\n大家識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:32:26.000Z","msg":"Do you hear the people sing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332beda05c1cbed42ad00ccd95c4745a253e70de","tid":1355980,"uid":182047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62abf74530b20576e90d7a5093ee7388b8df9ce9","tid":1355980,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:21:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42496dcfe79b51c511f335319870ca31570eb320","tid":1355980,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:46:25.000Z","msg":"大家記得戴口罩"},{"pid":"c45263bfa0a75b2d2b681d7142a590fe47babbdb","tid":1355980,"uid":282925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"